{"text_id":66715,"tokens":["As"," the"," summer"," break"," approaches",","," students"," often"," find"," themselves"," facing"," a"," dilemma"," -"," to"," indulge"," in"," leisure"," activities"," or"," to"," engage"," in"," productive"," learning"," experiences"," that"," foster"," continual"," growth"," and"," development","."," One"," effective"," way"," to"," promote"," learning"," during"," the"," summer"," break"," is"," through"," student","-","designed"," summer"," projects","."," In"," contrast"," to"," teacher","-","designed"," projects",","," which"," can"," be"," rigid"," and"," pres","criptive",","," student","-","designed"," projects"," offer"," a"," more"," effective"," approach"," to"," promoting"," continual"," learning"," and"," growth"," of"," the"," mind",".","\n\n","First"," and"," foremost",","," student","-","designed"," projects"," allow"," students"," to"," take"," ownership"," of"," their"," learning"," experience","."," When"," students"," are"," given"," the"," autonomy"," to"," design"," their"," own"," projects",","," they"," are"," more"," invested"," in"," the"," outcome"," and"," are"," more"," likely"," to"," be"," motivated"," to"," learn","."," This"," autonomy"," also"," enables"," students"," to"," pursue"," topics"," that"," align"," with"," their"," interests"," and"," passions",","," making"," the"," learning"," experience"," more"," enjoyable"," and"," engaging","."," In"," contrast",","," teacher","-","designed"," projects"," can"," be"," restrictive"," and"," may"," not"," cater"," to"," individual"," students","'"," interests",","," leading"," to"," a"," lack"," of"," enthusiasm"," and"," motivation",".","\n\n","Another"," significant"," advantage"," of"," student","-","designed"," projects"," is"," that"," they"," promote"," critical"," thinking",","," creativity",","," and"," problem","-","solving"," skills","."," When"," students"," are"," tasked"," with"," designing"," their"," own"," projects",","," they"," must",